      "name": "Hemolysis index comparison across five operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at five flow-speed combinations. Monte Carlo sampling over rheological parameters and inlet boundary conditions was performed; 95 % prediction intervals reported. Structured UQ node captures aleatory contributions from blood property variability.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/monte-carlo-nih-5op"
