      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution validation — qualitative variability assessment",
      "description": "Wall shear stress (WSS) distributions from CFD compared against PIV-derived estimates at the impeller tip region. Cycle-to-cycle flow variability and inter-specimen geometric variability are acknowledged as sources of aleatory uncertainty; however, inherent variability was assessed qualitatively through engineering judgement rather than through a formal probabilistic UQ procedure. No structured uncertainty quantification node is linked to this result."
    },
